        <h2>
            王立群读《史记》之秦始皇（下）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 3 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5265304">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5265304/" class="title-link">绚烂又短暂的一生</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5265304"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/efa7378/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1282388-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/efa7378/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">阿卡</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-12"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-12 01:04:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5265304_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  秦始皇 13岁登基 22岁亲政 39岁统一 49岁over  别人要花几辈子才能完成的事，他50年就做完了～ 跟乔布斯一样，偏执，短暂，绚烂。  这一切都来自于他的控制欲。  首先他要控制国家，所以他摆脱了吕不韦，赵姬，先控制了秦国；听从了李斯意见广纳各国人才，跟王翦道歉，采纳了尉...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
